you, Giancarlo, okay, bye.

08:25.159 --> 08:27.990
[traffic passing]

08:43.695 --> 08:47.872
[speaking foreign
language on TV]

09:15.140 --> 09:17.315
[sighing]

09:19.800 --> 09:21.837
What do I really want?

09:21.871 --> 09:24.460
[gentle music]

09:35.298 --> 09:37.956
[phone dialing]

09:42.478 --> 09:45.032
[phone ringing]

09:45.067 --> 09:46.758
Hey, it's me.

09:53.178 --> 09:54.732
-Hey.
-Hey.

09:56.043 --> 09:57.597
I was not expecting the call.

09:58.770 --> 10:01.428
Well, I been thinking a
lot about what you say.

10:01.462 --> 10:04.707
When you asked,
what do I wanna do?

10:04.742 --> 10:08.297
And what I wanna do
is have a nice walk

10:08.331 --> 10:09.781
and a good conversation.

10:10.989 --> 10:12.646
So, hope you don't
disappoint me.

10:14.544 --> 10:15.476
Ouch.

10:17.340 --> 10:20.930
So, the date wasn't
that great, huh?

10:20.965 --> 10:24.175
It was fine, I guess.
He was a nice guy.

10:25.555 --> 10:27.281
Do you date a lot?

10:27.316 --> 10:29.214
Mm, not much.

10:29.249 --> 10:30.457
I'm always busy.

10:31.561 --> 10:32.390
Working?

10:33.702 --> 10:34.530
Yeah.

10:35.600 --> 10:36.808
What do you do?

10:38.845 --> 10:41.261
I am a lawyer, a
business lawyer.

10:41.295 --> 10:44.574
Ooh, that sounds busy.

10:44.609 --> 10:46.438
Yes, it can get a little hectic.

10:47.923 --> 10:49.131
What do you do?

10:50.339 --> 10:52.444
What do I do, or
if I date or not?

10:54.067 --> 10:54.861
-Both.
-[laughs]

10:56.483 --> 10:58.727
I'm an app developer.

10:58.761 --> 11:02.247
I have my own company, and no,

11:02.282 --> 11:04.215
