11:05.354 --> 11:06.079
Hm.

11:07.149 --> 11:09.392
And what type of apps do you do?

11:09.427 --> 11:12.119
I'm actually developing
a very cool one.

11:12.154 --> 11:13.327
But this one, I'm
doing it for myself,

11:13.362 --> 11:15.882
not for any company,
I do freelance.

11:15.916 --> 11:18.263
I call it Mentira.

11:18.298 --> 11:21.232
It's kind of a lie detector
for your cellphone.

11:21.266 --> 11:24.925
It detects your voice,
like the steadiness of it,

11:24.960 --> 11:27.238
and then decides if you're
telling the truth or not.

11:27.272 --> 11:29.171
Hm, sounds interesting.

11:29.205 --> 11:31.069
But how does it work?

11:31.104 --> 11:33.796
It just speaks
through the speakers,

11:33.831 --> 11:37.110
the cellphone speakers,
and then it would say

11:37.144 --> 11:38.905
like "lie" or "true."

11:43.219 --> 11:46.947
So, why don't you date
that much anymore?

11:48.431 --> 11:52.712
It's not that I don't date
or I don't like to date.

11:52.746 --> 11:56.060
It just doesn't
interest me as much.

11:56.094 --> 11:58.994
Like the other older I
get, the more I realize

11:59.028 --> 12:02.480
that I waste more time
dating than not dating.

12:04.793 --> 12:06.518
Hm, what do you mean?

12:07.830 --> 12:09.867
If I date because
I need to date,

12:09.901 --> 12:12.766
