my time and money.

12:14.216 --> 12:17.978
If I'm not doing it, I do a
lot of things that I love.

12:18.013 --> 12:21.879
And the older I get, the
more the things that I love

12:21.913 --> 12:23.259
that I wanna do.

12:24.467 --> 12:28.092
Okay, but what if
time keeps passing

12:28.126 --> 12:30.025
and you don't find
your soulmate?

12:30.059 --> 12:31.785
