12:31.820 --> 12:32.752
No.

12:32.786 --> 12:34.823
You know what, that
would be fantastic.

12:34.857 --> 12:35.685
What?

12:35.720 --> 12:37.066
Because it means
I did what I love

12:37.101 --> 12:37.964
with the time that I had.

12:39.103 --> 12:43.866
You know, in time, I love to be

12:43.901 --> 12:46.662
in an empty room, I
love the quietness

12:46.696 --> 12:48.491
and the solitude of a space.

12:49.389 --> 12:50.528
It gives me peace.

12:51.391 --> 12:53.255
You say that.

12:53.289 --> 12:56.189
But the reality is that
nobody wants to be alone.

12:56.223 --> 12:57.431
Nobody wants to be.

12:59.399 --> 13:00.607
That's why you're here.

13:01.850 --> 13:04.438
No, I'm here because
I wanna be here,

13:04.473 --> 13:06.130
not because I don't
wanna be alone.

13:08.442 --> 13:12.584
I, I learned over time
to be honest with myself,

13:12.619 --> 13:17.279
